date 10-12-2025
time 11:34
1. Structural & Layout Improvements
Rewrote all HTML pages (Home, About, Products, Services, FAQ, Contact, Shop Now).
Unified header and footer across all pages.
Replaced incorrect file paths and fixed broken navigation links.
Corrected improper HTML nesting and indentation.
Implemented responsive layout using clean CSS structure.
Removed redundant classes, inline styles, and repeated elements.

 2. Navigation & Interactivity
Added fully functional mobile hamburger menu.
Added smooth slide animation for responsive navigation.
Standardized navigation design across all pages.

 3. SEO Enhancements
Added meta title, description, and keywords to every page.
Improved image filenames to SEO-friendly format (greenleaf-vegetables.webp).
Added meaningful and accessible alt text for all images.

 4. Dynamic & Interactive Elements
Implemented a working live search bar with dropdown suggestions.
Added FAQ accordion interactions using JavaScript.
Added Google Map embed on Contact page with custom marker.
Added image gallery lightbox with next/previous controls.
Added dynamic footer year (auto-updates every year).

 5. Forms & Validation
Built a complete contact form (Name, Email, Subject, Message).
Added JavaScript front-end validation.
Implemented email recipient processing using mailto: and backend-ready structure.
Improved browser validation styling.

 6. Shop & Products
Redid product layout using a clean grid system.
Added hover effects, consistent card design, and responsive spacing
Improved “Add to Cart” and CTA buttons.

 7. CSS Improvements
Organized full stylesheet using variables, reset, layout, components, and utilities.
Fixed color palette consistency.
Removed unused selectors and optimized CSS for performance.
Added media queries for tablet and mobile layouts.

 8. JavaScript Enhancements
Rewrote script.js with ES6 standards.
Added code sections for:
Hamburger menu toggle
Search suggestions
Lightbox
Accordion
Dynamic year
Form handling
Clean comments and structure for readability.

9. Image Optimization
Converted large images to WebP.
Reduced file size for faster loading.
Upated all <img> to use descriptive alt attributes.

 10. Accessibility Improvements
Added aria-expanded, aria-controls for accordions.
Added descriptive alt text.
Improved color contrast.
Proper HTML5 semantics added (header, main, footer, nav).

