7. Challenges Faced
Correcting missing meta tags required restructuring the <head> of all pages.
Search functionality needed complete rewriting to support suggestions and filtering.
Contact form integration required JavaScript-based email service.
Responsive design required adjustments to layout and navigation.

8. Solutions Implemented
Centralized JavaScript file to control all dynamic features
Added JSON-like product structure for easier updates
Rebuilt navigation to include a hamburger menu
Added proper semantic HTML for SEO and accessibility
Integrated EmailJS for email processing
Created gallery using Lightbox.js

