10. Conclusion
The website successfully meets all requirements.
All missing elements have been fully implemented, including search, SEO, interactive features, contact form, dynamic content, and gallery.
The project now reflects a complete, user-friendly, responsive, accessible, and professional-grade website suitable for submission and real-world use.